---
title: Herby Caramelised Onion Lamb Shortloin with Roasted Rainbow Carrots & Wedges
description: This tender and flavourful cut of lamb is too good to miss, with a sticky-sweet and savoury glaze coating all over. Serve it with roasted baby veg and crispy potato wedges for the ultimate combo - all of our dinner-time dreams are coming true.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
